<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefef5a0d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s6814"><num value="6814">§ 6814.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idefef5a0e-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s6814/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated for each fiscal year such sums as are necessary to carry out this chapter.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idefef5a0f-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s6814/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Administrative expenses</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Funds appropriated under subsection (a) may not be used for the payment of the expenses or expenditures of the PromoFlor Council in administering a provision of an order.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idefef5a10-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/190/s15">Pub. L. 103–190, § 15</ref>, <date date="1993-12-14">Dec. 14, 1993</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/107/2289">107 Stat. 2289</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
